INSERT INTO `infrastructure` VALUES (1,3,'Smart classrooms','<p>Interactive whiteboards are used for classroom teaching and involve students to <strong>learn with technology</strong>. It helps in better comprehension of the concepts. This upgraded integration provides an advanced teaching atmosphere by connecting students to global information and better visual explanations.</p>','/images/infra/0718e59e-9f29-4efe-8d3e.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(2,3,'Computer Lab','<p>The school has a well-equipped <strong>computer lab</strong> for primary, middle, and secondary school. Every effort is being made to utilize the available facilities and develop computer awareness in each and every student. Computer learning has been recognized as an essential and useful tool of modern learning. All labs are air-conditioned and equipped with fire-fighting systems. All the Computer Labs are equipped with the latest hardware and software as per the curriculum.</p>','/images/infra/00e82116-ef3b-4b3c-82e1.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(3,3,'Science Lab','<p>Provides an open environment for students to experiment and do research work.</p>','/images/infra/f7161115-d6b7-4513-9b83.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(4,3,'Geography ground','<p>To provide tools vital to modern geographic analysis and thus create interest in the subject, offered as an optional subject.<br>&nbsp;</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(5,3,'Maths Lab','<p>Encourages the student to think and assimilate mathematical concepts in a more effective manner.<br>&nbsp;</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(6,3,'Library','<p>Vast collection of books to provide access to a rich array of stories, ideas and information.<br>&nbsp;</p>','/images/infra/a33d9a34-fe2d-42a8-9ce1.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(7,3,'Activity hall','<p>A vibrant place to provide wings to the thoughts of our students.<br>&nbsp;</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(8,3,'Sport room & playgrounds','<p>A wide plethora of indoor and outdoor games. CES conducts Evening school training sessions for students in basket ball, skating, chess, Volley Ball, Kabaddi, Shooting, and badminton. In recent years school team has bagged many prizes at inter-school, district, and national level tournaments.</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(9,3,'Amphi Theater','<p>An open-air venue to conduct classes in a different environment, is also used for presentations and programs.<br>&nbsp;</p>','/images/infra/7df4867a-8206-4e76-879a.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(10,3,'Staff rooms','<p>The teachers\' lounge equipped with facilities for effective planning.</p><p>STD:- 1 TO 5</p><p>STD:- 6 TO 10</p><p>STD:- 11, 12 Science and Commerce</p><p>&nbsp;</p>','/images/infra/a2a4c336-1f6e-457d-bef6.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(11,3,'Assembly ground','<p>A much-awaited place by students as each morning brings a new thought, igniting their minds.<br>&nbsp;</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(12,3,'Kids pool and Play ground','<p>To develop fine motor skills of our tiny tots.<br>&nbsp;</p>','/images/infra/9c5509a0-7ce0-49a5-93a8.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(13,3,'Clubs','<p>To bring out the hidden talents of our children we offer creative, oratorical, dramatics, nature, fine arts, gardening, reading, health and wellness, maths, science, Katha, riyaz, and harmony club.<br>&nbsp;</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(14,3,'Activity room','<p>We have yoga, aerobics, dance, art &amp; craft, and a music room for the holistic development of children. To bring out the hidden talents of our children we offer creative, oratorical, dramatics, nature, fine arts, gardening, Katha, riyaz, and harmony</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(15,3,'Atal Tinkering Lab','<p>ATL is a workspace where young minds can give shape to their ideas through hands-on do-it-yourself mode; and master innovation skills. Young children will get an opportunity to work with tools and equipment so as to comprehend the concepts of STEAM (Science, Technology, Engineering, and Math). ATL will have educational and learning do it yourself kits and equipment on  science, electronics, robotics, open-source microcontroller boards, sensors, and 3D printers and computers. Moreover, the other desirable facilities are meeting rooms and video conferencing. In order to foster inventiveness among students, ATL will conduct different activities ranging from regional and national level competitions, exhibitions, workshops on problem-solving, designing and fabrication of products, lecture series, etc. at periodic intervals</p>','/images/infra/4d1276fd-a2e7-4409-a810.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(16,3,'Physic Lab','<p>The Physics Laboratory is also well equipped with all the apparatus and equipment as per the G.S.E.B. syllabus requirement. Students are directed and encouraged to undertake experiments themselves, though supervision is done by experienced and trained faculty members. The lab also has a darkroom to perform experiments.</p>','/images/infra/6e1ecf60-f4d1-434f-b85e.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(17,3,'Chemistry Lab','<p>We have a well-equipped and spacious Chemistry Laboratory with the capacity to accommodate 50 students. We provide the latest facilities to students for qualitative as well as quantitative analysis according to the G.S.E.B. syllabus. Students learn and absorb much more through pragmatic experiments under the supervision of well-qualified and experienced faculty members.</p>','/images/infra/e04a9913-85a5-4be5-9647.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(18,3,'Biology Lab','<p>With a seating capacity of 40 students, the Biology Laboratory is equipped with modern equipment and apparatus like Projection Microscope and Binoculars. Students learn different concepts of the living world through models and specimens available in the Biology Laboratory.</p>','/images/infra/5f621371-86a5-4b25-b141.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(19,3,'Infrastructure','<p>The school has a 10-foot high boundary wall around the school premises which has been increased with a 3-4 feet chain link to enhance the security of the institution.<br>Cameras have been installed in the classrooms, laboratories, and office, as well as in the corridor for the safety of the students. Cameras have also been installed at the Main Gate of CES as well as in the Parking Area which covers the entire campus ensuring complete safety for students and staff.</p><ul><li>Each classroom has window grills and mosquito nets for the ground floor.</li><li>Laboratories are well-equipped to handle common emergencies.</li><li>The sports room is spacious, well-ventilated, and well-equipped to handle common sports injuries.</li><li>The secluded corners, corridors, and staircases are scrutinized by staff.</li><li>A direct intercom system is installed for speedy communication among authorized persons.</li><li>A multi-purpose public address system is installed to make public announcements in case of an emergency.</li><li>Staircases and exits are constructed as per the safety norms.</li></ul>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(20,3,'Bus Facility','<p>All norms and guidelines as per R.T.O. have complied for the school buses.</p>','/images/infra/9853ba95-3129-449a-9616.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(21,3,'Emergency Situations','<p>Fire Extinguishers and essential Fire Hydrants are placed in the school at various locations and maintained regularly.<br>A fire evacuation plan is displayed at different places in the building. Students know and understand the evacuation plan to avoid stampedes in case of disaster. Regular mock drills are conducted.<br>Emergency helpline numbers are displayed at prominent places on the school premises. An alarm system with sound modulation to alert is in place for all kinds of contingencies. Mock drill practice and observations are taken, and follow-up is done on a regular basis. Disaster management training in case of fire, earthquake, and other emergencies has been provided to the staff, senior students, and security personnel.<br>Regular preventive checks to ensure safety related to higher risk areas electrical, fire, civil work, school gates, transport, etc.</p>','/images/infra/a7827561-1ef6-4aa8-a4a2.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(22,3,'Workshops/Seminars','<p>Right from the Pre-Primary Section, children are made aware of Good Touch and Bad Touch. Self-defense workshops, first-aid training, and medical checkups, by well-trained personnel, are regularly organized for the staff members. Self-defense training is given to the girl students.</p>','undefined','2023-01-07',NULL),(23,3,'Health And Hygiene','<p>Provision for RO drinking water and quality is ensured by regular chemical analysis of water samples.<br>Health reports are maintained by the school.<br>Dental, pediatric, and eye checkups are done.<br>Adult education programs are conducted for students to ensure emotional stability and hygiene during the adolescence period.</p>','/images/infra/b2a8606f-b271-444b-a292.jpg','2023-01-07','2023-08-19'),(26,24,'ACTIVITIES','<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ACTIVITIES</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Parents Meeting (વાલીમિટિંગ)&nbsp;</strong></li><li><strong>Drawing/Painting Competition (ચિત્રસ્પર્ધા)</strong></li><li><strong>Handwriting Competition (સુલેખન&nbsp;સ્પર્ધા)&nbsp;</strong></li><li><strong>Mahendi Competition (મહેંદી&nbsp;સ્પર્ધા)</strong></li><li><strong>Essay Competition (નિબંધ&nbsp;સ્પર્ધા)</strong></li><li><strong>Guru Purnima Celebration (ગુરુપૂર્ણિમા&nbsp;ઉત્સવની&nbsp;ઉજવણી) &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><strong>Story Telling Competition (વાર્તાકથન&nbsp;સ્પર્ધા)</strong></li><li><strong>Book Review Competition (બુકરિવ્યુ&nbsp;કાર્યક્રમ)</strong></li><li><strong>Matki Decoration Compet