y area, proposition area.</li><li>Giving plan codes and manuals to tests/reference.</li><li>The library interfaces with various data organizations to give simple admittance to e-sources/information to additional clients so they could get to the ideal data even from their work environment.</li><li>By acquiring complete scope of records including books, compositions, diaries, magazines, paper and so forth on different subjects.</li><li>It additionally gives amusement and solid relaxation to client by giving various papers, magazines, brief tale books, web office and so on.</li><li>It gives reference administration through reference segment to lay out a contact between the right peruser and the right report in an individual manner to draw in additional clients.</li><li>Giving of copy, printing offices.</li><li>To keep up with and work a framework that permits, in addition to other things, reasonable review, documentation, capacity, conservation and exploration conditions.</li></ul><p><strong>Timing:&nbsp;</strong></p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Working days:&nbsp;</td><td>9:50 A.M. to 3:40 P.M.</td></tr><tr><td>Circulation Hours:</td><td>9:50 A.M. to 3:40 P.M.</td></tr><tr><td>Xerox Timings:</td><td>9:50 A.M. to 3:40 P.M.</td></tr><tr><td>Internet Timings:</td><td>9:50 A.M. to 3:40 P.M.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p>','/images/infra/1a0e9914-4537-419a-84a8.jpeg','2023-10-11','2023-10-11'),(197,13,'Medical fecilities','<ul><li>We care for our staff and students\' health and wellness. We believe that healthy minds produce productive results.</li><li>Our campus arranges blood donation and medical camps regularly, and the campus is also equipped with a first-aid centre that is equipped with needed medicine and other necessary things. Health insurance is also provided to the staff for medical emergencies.</li><li>Women\'s safety and care are our top priorities. We facilitated a separate, well-furnished lady waiting room with necessary amenities. Ladies can take rest when they are sick after taking the required first aid.</li></ul>','/images/infra/e8976089-26d8-4d57-8164.jpeg','2023-10-13',NULL),(200,13,'ATM and banking facilities','<ul><li>24 hours State Bank of India and Indian Overseas Bank ATMs are available near the college campus for smooth money transactions for students and staff.</li></ul>','/images/infra/f3dda60f-8117-44ae-9755.jpeg','2023-10-13','2023-10-13');
